title: Failing Upwards is Now Throwing Fits or: Two Grown Dirtbags Fumble the Bag at the 1 Yard Line
description:
The boys are back in town! Failing Upwards is now Throwing Fits. Here’s how it all went down. Plus, the trial of Cheffrey Epstein, a ton of housekeeping, and how Chuck bricked his interview with the Safdie bros, the filmmakers behind Uncut Gems.
